Program: Discovery
Title: Sacred Showdown - the science of belief
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jry0x
Last Broadcast Date: 22 February 2002
For centuries science and religion have not been on speaking terms. The programme looks at the long-standing tensions between science and religion and the initiatives to try and resolve them. Scientists investigate the nature of mystical experience and theologians examine the moral implications of new research. Show less